Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Southgate Towers represent the commercial hub of the iconic Southgate, Melbourne’s renowned restaurant and shopping precinct. Located at the gateway to Melbourne’s CBD, Southgate offers unrivalled amenity with restaurants, bars, cafes and accommodation at your doorstep.

The location offers excellent access close to all major arterials and public transport; Flinders Street Station less than 300 steps away and additional tram networks along St Kilda Road. There a number of bike paths surrounding Southbank linking to the southern, northern and eastern suburbs of Melbourne.

Southgate Towers offers A-Grade accommodation and has recently undergone a comprehensive repositioning and refurbishment program to create an exciting, modern and vibrant workplace for occupiers.

Key features of the repositioning include:

- A recent ground floor foyer upgrade featuring timber facades offering a refreshed corporate entry into the complex including a café operator for occupiers 
- Each of the lift lobbies have been tastefully refurbished to a modern design showcasing bespoke lighting and timber features
- State of the art end of trip facilities including; showers, change-rooms, extensive bike storage and lockers. 
- Modern on-floor refurbishments – including new ceiling, new lights, new carpet, feature black window frames and bespoke tiles around the core. 
- We have recently attracted large global and local multinational businesses such as HWT, IBM, LinkedIn, Dairy Australia and JB Hi-Fi. 
- Additionally, there is a large commercial car park on site run by Wilson Parking, to cater for all tenants and visitors.

Available Areas

Whole floors available at 40 City Road:
Level 22: 1,161sqm - Refurbished whole floor
Level 23: 1,171sqm - Refurbished whole floor


Suites available at 60 City Road:
-Level 12: 325sqm - Brand new fitted and furnished suite 
-Level 10: 421sqm - Brand new fitted and furnished suite
-Level 7:  200 - 460sqm - Brand new fitted and furbished suites
-Level 6: 391sqm - Brand new fitted and furnished suite

This is an exceptional and unique opportunity not to be missed!

For further information and to arrange an inspection, please contact the listed agents.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Proudly positioned on Clarendon Street’s city end, OneFourFive Southbank is an agile commercial space designed for future-focused businesses. This is a contemporary environment that reimagines the workspace, offering flexibly designed interiors, a light-filled open stairwell and generous outdoor terraces to promote collaboration and foster wellbeing.

OneFourFive provides excellent access to public transport and major cycling routes including the Main Yarra Trail. To support a modern ride-to-work culture, OneFourFive has ample bike parking spaces, enabling an environmentally friendly and active trip to the office.

Open spaces and large windows allow natural light to spill across each floor. Outdoor terraces provide the ideal place for meetings and gatherings with colleagues on sunny days and warm evenings.

At ground level, the entrance will activate the area, connecting staff and businesses to the local community.

– Multiple bike parking (21 bicycle racks)
– End of trip facilities (44 lockers)
– 6 showers in End of Trip
– Contemporary open plan
– Meeting desks and booth seating
– Generous open circulation spaces
– Outdoor protected terraces on various levels
– Ground floor activation or retail space

Available space:
Ground floor- 158sqm
Level 1- 386sqm
Level 2- 386sqm
Level 3- 319sqm
Level 4- 319sqm
Level 5- 197sqm
Level 6- 197sqm
Whole building- 1962sqm

Please call Josh or Anthony for further information or check out our dedicated website: https://www.onefourfiveclarendon.com.au/

Southbank is home to Melbourne’s premium arts and entertainment venues, including the Melbourne’s Arts Precinct – one of the largest art precincts in the world, Crown Melbourne, renowned restaurants and bars and the Royal Botanic Gardens.
28 Freshwater Place is within immediate proximity to all major modes of public transportation, including the CBD’s busiest train station, Flinders Street, and beyond that the future new Town Hall train station.

The building has undergone works to upgrade the End of Trip (EOT) and wellness facilities, creating a ‘Japanese-inspired’ state-of-the-art amenity for tenants including 194 bikes, 24 showers and 394 lockers.
Boasting large podium floors plates which are bright and benefit from an efficient side service core design to accommodate tenant requirements today and into the future.

Building Features include:
-6 Star NABERS indoor environment & 5.5 Star NABERS energy rating
-Floor to ceiling glass providing exceptional natural light and views
-Excellent transport linkages
-Exceptional surrounding food and recreation amenity 
-State of the art EOT facilities

Tenancy Features include:
-Area’s available from 1,780-5,340sqm 
-Fully fitted floors available with interconnecting staircase 
-Available immediately 
-Flexible lease terms available 
-On floor showers
-Large workstations providing good social distancing
-Great combination of open plan and enclosed offices, quiet rooms and meeting rooms
-Large kitchen/breakout on Level 23 offering panoramic views back to the CBD


For further information please contact the listing agents.
